latestIgtvVideos.title: 🌟WEEKLY SKINCARE ROUTINE🌟
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
🍀Step 1: GREEN TEA STEAM- it soothes irritated skin, has anti-ageing properties, prevent wrinkles, fine lines and other skin diseases, detoxifies your pores and keep your skin hydrated.
🍀Step 2: Using @st.ivesarabia blemish control apricot scrub. It exfoliates and sloughs off dead skin and boosts blood circulation - giving you that glow.
🍀Step 3: Mix Honey and Turmeric. Using @miniso_uae silicon brush. Honey reduces acne and the inflammation and redness it causes. Turmeric works as an antiseptic that maintains the pH levels of your skin, reducing acne. It also helps to restore natural glow and treats uneven skin tone.
🍀Step 4 - Rinse the pack with mild cleanser. Using @joveesherbal (optional) if you think the turmeric left stain on your skin. If no stains, then wash it with normal water.
🍀Step 5- Rub ice cubes on your face and neck to close/ tighten your pores.
🍀Step 6- Apply your moisturizer. I’m using @neutrogename hydro boost moisturizer and @labello_me lip balm.
🌟GLOW THIS WINTER AND LOVE YOUR SELF!🌟
🔴Patch test necessary if you think you can be allergic to these products!🔴
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Graduation’19🎓
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Here is a small video of one of the most memorable days in my life, @middlesexdubai graduation’19🎓

Hope you all enjoy the video! 
As sad as you are to say goodbye to your college life, you can't wait to step out into the real world.

Thinking of all the hard work we put in: the countless hours of reading, the term papers, the sleepless nights, University activities and events. It was all over in the blink of an eye. We finally got to put on our gown, switch over our tassel, and throw our cap into the air in celebration. I’ll miss you all. Congratulations to all of you again!❣️🎓
